name: Anything Goes - Preview
description:
A game made from suggestions of my community and followers on TikTok, suggestions such as "Ramen with Legs", "Waluigi Throwing it Back", "Danny Devito" and "Spongebob riding a Unicorn in the sky while it rains cows". Its kinda a wild ride. The story makes no sense, theres no theme, its not serious in any way. Just push play and let it do its thing because half of the time it will do what it wants rather than what you tell it. 

Feel free to come join on Tiktok: williamalexandercraig

This game is in development, this is a preview of the current development of the game and will be updated as i add more suggestions.
